Package it.uniroma2.sel.simlab.jeqn.users

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    TokenCarrier
    Defines the interface every token carrier user has to conform.
    UserGenerator
    Defines the interface every user generator has to conform
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Category
    Implements Category, that represents a class of users within EQN network.
    CloneUser
    Represents a clone user of an "original" user passing through a Split node.
    CloneUser_UserTracker
    Represents a CloneUser with tracking capabilities.
    CountingUser
    Represents a user that incorporates counting capabilities, ie the user is provided with an internal counter.
    DadUser
    Defines the Dad User, ie any type of jEQN user that passing through a Fork Node is transformed in a Dad User - and associated to a set of Son Users
    Link  
    MultiCatUserGenerator
    Provides a multi category generator.
    SameCatUserGenerator
    Provides a User generator for a specified category of users.
    SingleCatUserGenerator
    Provides a user generator for a single given user category
    SonUser
    Defines a SonUser, ie a user created by a Fork Node upon the arrival of any jEQN user.
    SonUserGenerator
    Provides a generator of son users from a given dad user
    TrackingPathUser
    Defines a user with path tracking capabilities.
    User
    Implements the basic user in jEQN simulator
    UserWithCounter
    Wraps a user allowing it to set up a counter
    UserWithTokens<T extends Token>
    Wraps a user allowing it to carry some tokens.
